一. 设备仿真原理SPI

        SPI和I2C一样也是很常用的串行通信协议，并且框架都很类似，都分主机控制器驱动和设备驱动，主机控制器也就是SOC的SPI控制器接口，一般linux内核都自带主机控制器，我们要做的就是SPI设备驱动。

1.设备添加

下面是QEMU自带的SPI模拟程序，位于\qemu\hw\ssi\imx_spi.c，可以看到当我们SPI驱动写数据时，QEMU会把接收到的数据push进tx_fifo写缓存，然后传入imx_spi_flush_txfifo函数，再由次函数push进rx_fifo，也就是读缓存。

  1. static const struct MemoryRegionOps imx_spi_ops = {
  2.     .read = imx_spi_read,
  3.     .write = imx_spi_write,
  4.     .endianness = DEVICE_NATIVE_ENDIAN,
  5.     .......
  6. };
  7.  
  8.  
  9. static void imx_spi_write(void *opaque, hwaddr offset, uint64_t value,
  10.                            unsigned size)
  11. {
  12.     IMXSPIState *s = opaque;
  13.     uint32_t index = offset >> 2;
  14.     uint32_t change_mask;
  15.  
  16.     if (index >=  ECSPI_MAX) {
  17.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_GUEST_ERROR, "[%s]%s: Bad register at offset 0x%"
  18.                       HWADDR_PRIx "\n", TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__, offset);
  19.         return;
  20.     }
  21.  
  22.     if (value)
  23.         DPRINTF("reg[%s] <= 0x%" PRIx32 "\n", imx_spi_reg_name(index),
  24.             (uint32_t)value);
  25.  
  26.     change_mask = s->regs[index] ^ value;
  27.  
  28.     switch (index) {
  29.     case ECSPI_RXDATA:
  30.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_GUEST_ERROR, "[%s]%s: Trying to write to RX FIFO\n",
  31.                       TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__);
  32.         break;
  33.     case ECSPI_TXDATA:
  34.         if (!imx_spi_is_enabled(s)) {
  35.             /* Ignore writes if device is disabled */
  36.             break;
  37.         } else if (fifo32_is_full(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  38.             /* Ignore writes if queue is full */
  39.             break;
  40.         }
  41.  
  42.         fifo32_push(&s->tx_fifo, (uint32_t)value);
  43.  
  44.         if (imx_spi_channel_is_master(s) &&
  45.             (s->regs[ECSPI_CONREG] & ECSPI_CONREG_SMC)) {
  46.             /*
  47.              * Start emitting if current channel is master and SMC bit is
  48.              * set.
  49.              */
  50.             imx_spi_flush_txfifo(s); // 从SPI驱动接收到的数据写缓存
  51.         }
  52.  
  53.         break;
  54.     case ECSPI_STATREG:
  55.         /* the RO and TC bits are write-one-to-clear */
  56.         value &= ECSPI_STATREG_RO | ECSPI_STATREG_TC;
  57.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] &= ~value;
  58.  
  59.         break;
  60.     case ECSPI_CONREG:
  61.         s->regs[ECSPI_CONREG] = value;
  62.  
  63.         if (!imx_spi_is_enabled(s)) {
  64.             /* device is disabled, so this is a reset */
  65.             imx_spi_reset(DEVICE(s));
  66.             return;
  67.         }
  68.  
  69.         if (imx_spi_channel_is_master(s)) {
  70.             int i;
  71.  
  72.             /* We are in master mode */
  73.  
  74.             for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
  75.                 qemu_set_irq(s->cs_lines[i],
  76.                              i == imx_spi_selected_channel(s) ? 0 : 1);
  77.             }
  78.  
  79.             if ((value & change_mask & ECSPI_CONREG_SMC) &&
  80.                 !fifo32_is_empty(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  81.                 /* SMC bit is set and TX FIFO has some slots filled in */
  82.                 imx_spi_flush_txfifo(s);
  83.             } else if ((value & change_mask & ECSPI_CONREG_XCH) &&
  84.                 !(value & ECSPI_CONREG_SMC)) {
  85.                 /* This is a request to start emitting */
  86.                 imx_spi_flush_txfifo(s);
  87.             }
  88.         }
  89.  
  90.         break;
  91.     case ECSPI_MSGDATA:
  92.         /* it is not clear from the spec what MSGDATA is for */
  93.         /* Anyway it is not used by Linux driver */
  94.         /* So for now we just ignore it */
  95.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_UNIMP,
  96.                       "[%s]%s: Trying to write to MSGDATA, ignoring\n",
  97.                       TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__);
  98.         break;
  99.     default:
  100.         s->regs[index] = value;
  101.  
  102.         break;
  103.     }
  104.  
  105.     imx_spi_update_irq(s); // 设置ECPI的状态寄存器
  106. }
  107.  
  108.  
  109. static void imx_spi_flush_txfifo(IMXSPIState *s)
  110. {
  111.     uint32_t tx;
  112.     uint32_t rx;
  113.  
  114.     while (!fifo32_is_empty(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  115.         int tx_burst = 0;
  116.         int index = 0;
  117.  
  118.         if (s->burst_length <= 0) {
  119.             s->burst_length = imx_spi_burst_length(s);
  120.  
  121.             DPRINTF("Burst length = %d\n", s->burst_length);
  122.  
  123.             if (imx_spi_is_multiple_master_burst(s)) {
  124.                 s->regs[ECSPI_CONREG] |= ECSPI_CONREG_XCH;
  125.             }
  126.         }
  127.  
  128.         tx = fifo32_pop(&s->tx_fifo);
  129.  
  130.         DPRINTF("data tx:0x%08x\n", tx);
  131.  
  132.         tx_burst = MIN(s->burst_length, 32);
  133.  
  134.         rx = 0;
  135.  
  136.         while (tx_burst) {
  137.             uint8_t byte = tx & 0xff;
  138.             uint8_t byte_rx = byte;
  139.             DPRINTF("writing 0x%02x\n", (uint32_t)byte);
  140.  
  141.             /* We need to write one byte at a time */
  142.             byte = ssi_transfer(s->bus, byte);
  143.  
  144.             if (byte == 0) {
  145.                 byte = byte_rx;
  146.             }
  147.             DPRINTF("0x%02x read\n", (uint32_t)byte);
  148.             tx = tx >> 8;
  149.             rx |= (byte << (index * 8));
  150.  
  151.             /* Remove 8 bits from the actual burst */
  152.             tx_burst -= 8;
  153.             s->burst_length -= 8;
  154.             index++;
  155.         }
  156.         
  157.         DPRINTF("data rx:0x%08x\n", rx);
  158.  
  159.         if (fifo32_is_full(&s->rx_fifo)) {
  160.             s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_RO;
  161.         } else {
  162.             fifo32_push(&s->rx_fifo, (uint8_t)rx);
  163.         }
  164.  
  165.         if (s->burst_length <= 0) {
  166.             if (!imx_spi_is_multiple_master_burst(s)) {
  167.                 s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_TC;
  168.                 break;
  169.             }
  170.         }
  171.     }
  172.  
  173.     if (fifo32_is_empty(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  174.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_TC;
  175.         s->regs[ECSPI_CONREG] &= ~ECSPI_CONREG_XCH;
  176.     }
  177.  
  178.     /* TODO: We should also use TDR and RDR bits */
  179.  
  180.     DPRINTF("End: TX Fifo Size = %d, RX Fifo Size = %d\n",
  181.             fifo32_num_used(&s->tx_fifo), fifo32_num_used(&s->rx_fifo));
  182. }

当SPI驱动读取数据时，imx_spi_read读函数又把读缓存的数据pop出来并返回给SPI驱动。

  1.  
  2. static uint64_t imx_spi_read(void *opaque, hwaddr offset, unsigned size)
  3. {
  4.     uint32_t value = 0;
  5.     IMXSPIState *s = opaque;
  6.     uint32_t index = offset >> 2;
  7.  
  8.     if (index >=  ECSPI_MAX) {
  9.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_GUEST_ERROR, "[%s]%s: Bad register at offset 0x%"
  10.                       HWADDR_PRIx "\n", TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__, offset);
  11.         return 0;
  12.     }
  13.  
  14.     switch (index) {
  15.     case ECSPI_RXDATA:
  16.         if (!imx_spi_is_enabled(s)) {
  17.             value = 0;
  18.         } else if (fifo32_is_empty(&s->rx_fifo)) {
  19.             /* value is undefined */
  20.             value = 0xdeadbeef;
  21.         } else {
  22.             /* read from the RX FIFO */
  23.             value = fifo32_pop(&s->rx_fifo);
  24.         }
  25.         break;
  26.     case ECSPI_TXDATA:
  27.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_GUEST_ERROR, "[%s]%s: Trying to read from TX FIFO\n",
  28.                       TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__);
  29.  
  30.         /* Reading from TXDATA gives 0 */
  31.  
  32.         break;
  33.     case ECSPI_MSGDATA:
  34.         qemu_log_mask(LOG_GUEST_ERROR, "[%s]%s: Trying to read from MSG FIFO\n",
  35.                       TYPE_IMX_SPI, __func__);
  36.  
  37.         /* Reading from MSGDATA gives 0 */
  38.  
  39.         break;
  40.     default:
  41.         value = s->regs[index];
  42.         break;
  43.     }
  44.     if (value)
  45.        DPRINTF("reg[%s] => 0x%" PRIx32 "\n", imx_spi_reg_name(index), value);
  46.  
  47.     imx_spi_update_irq(s);
  48.  
  49.     return (uint64_t)value;
  50. }

不管是写函数还是读函数或者reset函数，最后一行都有imx_spi_update_irq，这是用来设置ECPI的状态寄存器，这个充分模拟了真实芯片SPI驱动内部的操作，如下图为SPI状态寄存器的结构图。

  1. static void imx_spi_update_irq(IMXSPIState *s)
  2. {
  3.     int level;
  4.  
  5.     if (fifo32_is_empty(&s->rx_fifo)) {
  6.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] &= ~ECSPI_STATREG_RR;
  7.     } else {
  8.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_RR;
  9.     }
  10.  
  11.     if (fifo32_is_full(&s->rx_fifo)) {
  12.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_RF;
  13.     } else {
  14.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] &= ~ECSPI_STATREG_RF;
  15.     }
  16.  
  17.     if (fifo32_is_empty(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  18.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_TE;
  19.     } else {
  20.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] &= ~ECSPI_STATREG_TE;
  21.     }
  22.  
  23.     if (fifo32_is_full(&s->tx_fifo)) {
  24.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] |= ECSPI_STATREG_TF;
  25.     } else {
  26.         s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] &= ~ECSPI_STATREG_TF;
  27.     }
  28.  
  29.     level = s->regs[ECSPI_STATREG] & s->regs[ECSPI_INTREG] ? 1 : 0;
  30.  
  31.     qemu_set_irq(s->irq, level);
  32.  
  33.     DPRINTF("IRQ level is %d\n", level);
  34. }

二.设备驱动开发

前面说了SPI驱动一般芯片厂商都写好了，SPI设备驱动就是对接设备所写的驱动，所以我们直接写设备驱动。

  1. pinctrl_ecspi3: icm20608 {
  2. 	fsl,pins = <
  3. 		MX6UL_PAD_UART2_RX_DATA__ECSPI3_SCLK       0x000010B1
  4.         MX6UL_PAD_UART2_CTS_B__ECSPI3_MOSI         0x000010B1
  5.         MX6UL_PAD_UART2_RTS_B__ECSPI3_MISO         0x000010B1
  6.         //MX6UL_PAD_UART1_CTS_B__GPIO1_IO18          0x000010B0 /*gpio cs0*/
  7. 		MX6UL_PAD_UART2_TX_DATA__GPIO1_IO20        0x000010B0 /*gpio cs1*/
  8.  
  9. 	>;
  10. };
  11.  
  12. &ecspi3 {
  13.    fsl,spi-num-chipselects = <1>;
  14.    cs-gpios = <&gpio1 20 0>;
  15.    pinctrl-names = "default";
  16.    pinctrl-0 = <&pinctrl_ecspi3>;
  17.    status = "okay";
  18.  
  19.    
  20.    spidev: icm20608@0 {
  21. 	  compatible = "icm20608";
  22.       reg = <0>;
  23.       spi-max-frequency = <8000000>;
  24.    };
  25.  
  26. };
  1.  
  2.  
  3. /*
  4.  * @description	: 从icm20608读取多个寄存器数据
  5.  * @param - dev:  icm20608设备
  6.  * @param - reg:  要读取的寄存器首地址
  7.  * @param - val:  读取到的数据
  8.  * @param - len:  要读取的数据长度
  9.  * @return 		: 操作结果
  10.  */
  11. static int icm20608_read_regs(struct icm20608_dev *dev, u8 reg, void *buf, int len)
  12. {
  13.  
  14. 	int ret = -1;
  15. 	unsigned char txdata[1];
  16. 	unsigned char * rxdata;
  17. 	struct spi_message m;
  18. 	struct spi_transfer *t;
  19. 	struct spi_device *spi = (struct spi_device *)dev->private_data;
  20.     
  21. 	t = kzalloc(sizeof(struct spi_transfer), GFP_KERNEL);	/* 申请内存 */
  22. 	if(!t) {
  23. 		return -ENOMEM;
  24. 	}
  25.  
  26. 	rxdata = kzalloc(sizeof(char) * len, GFP_KERNEL);	/* 申请内存 */
  27. 	if(!rxdata) {
  28. 		goto out1;
  29. 	}
  30.  
  31. 	/* 一共发送len+1个字节的数据，第一个字节为
  32. 	寄存器首地址，一共要读取len个字节长度的数据，*/
  33. 	txdata[0] = reg | 0x80;		/* 写数据的时候首寄存器地址bit8要置1 */			
  34. 	t->tx_buf = txdata;			/* 要发送的数据 */
  35.     t->rx_buf = rxdata;			/* 要读取的数据 */
  36. 	t->len = len+1;				/* t->len=发送的长度+读取的长度 */
  37. 	spi_message_init(&m);		/* 初始化spi_message */
  38. 	spi_message_add_tail(t, &m);/* 将spi_transfer添加到spi_message队列 */
  39. 	ret = spi_sync(spi, &m);	/* 同步发送 */
  40. 	if(ret) {
  41. 		goto out2;
  42. 	}
  43. 	
  44.     memcpy(buf , rxdata+1, len);  /* 只需要读取的数据 */
  45.  
  46. out2:
  47. 	kfree(rxdata);					/* 释放内存 */
  48. out1:	
  49. 	kfree(t);						/* 释放内存 */
  50. 	
  51. 	return ret;
  52. }
  53.  
  54.  
  55. /*
  56.  * @description	: 向icm20608多个寄存器写入数据
  57.  * @param - dev:  icm20608设备
  58.  * @param - reg:  要写入的寄存器首地址
  59.  * @param - val:  要写入的数据缓冲区
  60.  * @param - len:  要写入的数据长度
  61.  * @return 	  :   操作结果
  62.  */
  63. static s32 icm20608_write_regs(struct icm20608_dev *dev, u8 reg, u8 *buf, u8 len)
  64. {
  65. 	int ret = -1;
  66. 	unsigned char *txdata;
  67. 	struct spi_message m;
  68. 	struct spi_transfer *t;
  69. 	struct spi_device *spi = (struct spi_device *)dev->private_data;
  70. 	
  71. 	t = kzalloc(sizeof(struct spi_transfer), GFP_KERNEL);	/* 申请内存 */
  72. 	if(!t) {
  73. 		return -ENOMEM;
  74. 	}
  75. 	
  76. 	txdata = kzalloc(sizeof(char)+len, GFP_KERNEL);
  77. 	if(!txdata) {
  78. 		goto out1;
  79. 	}
  80. 	
  81. 	/* 一共发送len+1个字节的数据，第一个字节为
  82. 	寄存器首地址，len为要写入的寄存器的集合，*/
  83. 	*txdata = reg & ~0x80;	/* 写数据的时候首寄存器地址bit8要清零 */
  84.     memcpy(txdata+1, buf, len);	/* 把len个寄存器拷贝到txdata里，等待发送 */
  85. 	t->tx_buf = txdata;			/* 要发送的数据 */
  86. 	t->len = len+1;				/* t->len=发送的长度+读取的长度 */
  87. 	spi_message_init(&m);		/* 初始化spi_message */
  88. 	spi_message_add_tail(t, &m);/* 将spi_transfer添加到spi_message队列 */
  89. 	ret = spi_sync(spi, &m);	/* 同步发送 */
  90.     if(ret) {
  91.         goto out2;
  92.     }
  93. 	
  94. out2:
  95. 	kfree(txdata);				/* 释放内存 */
  96. out1:
  97. 	kfree(t);					/* 释放内存 */
  98. 	return ret;
  99. }
  100.  
  101. static void icm20608_write_onereg(struct icm20608_dev *dev, u8 reg, u8 value)
  102. {
  103. 	u8 buf = value;
  104. 	icm20608_write_regs(dev, reg, &buf, 1);
  105. }
  106.  
  107. /*
  108.  * @description		: 打开设备
  109.  * @param - inode 	: 传递给驱动的inode
  110.  * @param - filp 	: 设备文件，file结构体有个叫做pr似有ate_data的成员变量
  111.  * 					  一般在open的时候将private_data似有向设备结构体。
  112.  * @return 			: 0 成功;其他 失败
  113.  */
  114. static int icm20608_open(struct inode *inode, struct file *filp)
  115. {
  116. 	filp->private_data = &icm20608dev; /* 设置私有数据 */
  117. 	return 0;
  118. }
  119.  
  120. static unsigned char icm20608_read_onereg(struct icm20608_dev *dev, u8 reg)
  121. {
  122. 	u8 data = 0;
  123. 	icm20608_read_regs(dev, reg, &data, 1);
  124. 	return data;
  125. }
  126.  
  127. static ssize_t icm20608_read(struct file *filp, char __user *buf, size_t cnt, loff_t *off)
  128. {
  129.     unsigned char data[14] = { 0 };
  130. 	long err = 0;
  131. 	struct icm20608_dev *dev = (struct icm20608_dev *)filp->private_data;
  132.     icm20608_read_regs(dev, 0x6B, data, 14);
  133.     copy_to_user(buf, data, sizeof(data));
  134. 	if (data[0])
  135.     	printk("icm20608_read_regs = %#X\r\n", data[0]);
  136. 	return 0;
  137. }
  138.  
  139. static long icm20608_ioctl(struct file *filp, unsigned int cmd, unsigned long arg)
  140. {
  141. 	struct icm20608_dev *dev = (struct icm20608_dev *)filp->private_data;
  142.     icm20608_write_onereg(dev, cmd, arg);
  143. 	return 0;
  144. }
  145.  
  146. /*
  147.  * @description		: 关闭/释放设备
  148.  * @param - filp 	: 要关闭的设备文件(文件描述符)
  149.  * @return 			: 0 成功;其他 失败
  150.  */
  151. static int icm20608_release(struct inode *inode, struct file *filp)
  152. {
  153. 	return 0;
  154. }
  155.  
  156. /* icm20608操作函数 */
  157. static const struct file_operations icm20608_ops = {
  158. 	.owner = THIS_MODULE,
  159. 	.open = icm20608_open,
  160. 	.read = icm20608_read,
  161.     .unlocked_ioctl = icm20608_ioctl,
  162. 	.release = icm20608_release,
  163. };
  164.  
  165. /*
  166.  * ICM20608内部寄存器初始化函数 
  167.  * @param  	: 无
  168.  * @return 	: 无
  169.  */
  170. void icm20608_reginit(void)
  171. {
  172.     icm20608_write_onereg(&icm20608dev, 0x6B, 0x80);
  173.     return;
  174. }
  175.  
  176.  /*
  177.   * @description     : spi驱动的probe函数，当驱动与
  178.   *                    设备匹配以后此函数就会执行
  179.   * @param - client  : i2c设备
  180.   * @param - id      : i2c设备ID
  181.   * 
  182.   */	
  183. static int icm20608_probe(struct spi_device *spi)
  184. {
  185. 	/* 1、构建设备号 */
  186. 	if (icm20608dev.major) {
  187. 		icm20608dev.devid = MKDEV(icm20608dev.major, 0);
  188. 		register_chrdev_region(icm20608dev.devid, ICM20608_CNT, ICM20608_NAME);
  189. 	} else {
  190. 		alloc_chrdev_region(&icm20608dev.devid, 0, ICM20608_CNT, ICM20608_NAME);
  191. 		icm20608dev.major = MAJOR(icm20608dev.devid);
  192. 	}
  193.  
  194. 	/* 2、注册设备 */
  195. 	cdev_init(&icm20608dev.cdev, &icm20608_ops);
  196. 	cdev_add(&icm20608dev.cdev, icm20608dev.devid, ICM20608_CNT);
  197.  
  198. 	/* 3、创建类 */
  199. 	icm20608dev.class = class_create(THIS_MODULE, ICM20608_NAME);
  200. 	if (IS_ERR(icm20608dev.class)) {
  201. 		return PTR_ERR(icm20608dev.class);
  202. 	}
  203.  
  204. 	/* 4、创建设备 */
  205. 	icm20608dev.device = device_create(icm20608dev.class, NULL, icm20608dev.devid, NULL, ICM20608_NAME);
  206. 	if (IS_ERR(icm20608dev.device)) {
  207. 		return PTR_ERR(icm20608dev.device);
  208. 	}
  209.  
  210. 	/*初始化spi_device */
  211. 	spi->mode = SPI_MODE_0;	/*MODE0，CPOL=0，CPHA=0*/
  212. 	spi_setup(spi);
  213. 	icm20608dev.private_data = spi; /* 设置私有数据 */
  214. 	
  215.     //icm20608_reginit();
  216. 	return 0;
  217. }
  218.  
  219.  
  220. /*
  221.  * @description     : i2c驱动的remove函数，移除i2c驱动的时候此函数会执行
  222.  * @param - client 	: i2c设备
  223.  * @return          : 0，成功;其他负值,失败
  224.  */
  225. static int icm20608_remove(struct spi_device *spi)
  226. {
  227. 	/* 删除设备 */
  228. 	cdev_del(&icm20608dev.cdev);
  229. 	unregister_chrdev_region(icm20608dev.devid, ICM20608_CNT);
  230.  
  231. 	/* 注销掉类和设备 */
  232. 	device_destroy(icm20608dev.class, icm20608dev.devid);
  233. 	class_destroy(icm20608dev.class);
  234. 	return 0;
  235. }
  236.  
  237. /* 传统匹配方式ID列表 */
  238. static const struct spi_device_id icm20608_id[] = {
  239. 	{"alientek,icm20608", 0},  
  240. 	{}
  241. };
  242.  
  243. /* 设备树匹配列表 */
  244. static const struct of_device_id icm20608_of_match[] = {
  245. 	{ .compatible = "alientek,icm20608" },
  246. 	{ /* Sentinel */ }
  247. };
  248.  
  249. /* SPI驱动结构体 */	
  250. static struct spi_driver icm20608_driver = {
  251. 	.probe = icm20608_probe,
  252. 	.remove = icm20608_remove,
  253. 	.driver = {
  254. 			.owner = THIS_MODULE,
  255. 		   	.name = "icm20608",
  256. 		   	.of_match_table = icm20608_of_match, 
  257. 		   },
  258. 	.id_table = icm20608_id,
  259. };
  260. 		   
  261. /*
  262.  * @description	: 驱动入口函数
  263.  * @param 		: 无
  264.  * @return 		: 无
  265.  */
  266. static int __init icm20608_init(void)
  267. {
  268. 	return spi_register_driver(&icm20608_driver);
  269. }
  270.  
  271. /*
  272.  * @description	: 驱动出口函数
  273.  * @param 		: 无
  274.  * @return 		: 无
  275.  */
  276. static void __exit icm20608_exit(void)
  277. {
  278. 	spi_unregister_driver(&icm20608_driver);
  279. }
  280.  
  281. module_init(icm20608_init);
  282. module_exit(icm20608_exit);
  283.
